|   NULL |   NULL | j      |      0 | NULL   | NULL   | NULL   |   NULL |
|   NULL |   NULL | p      |      0 | NULL   | NULL   | NULL   |   NULL |
+--------+--------+--------+--------+--------+--------+--------+--------+

DROP TabLE IF EXISTS `a`;
DROP TabLE IF EXISTS `b`;
